  "body": "![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/6820/9319472/95990f74-4503-11e5-882e-e45f32d6fb85.png)\n\nHere's the code:\n\n``` js\nvar LeakyPortal = React.createClass({\n  render: function() {\n    return <div ref=\"div\" />;\n  },\n  componentDidMount: function() {\n    React.render(\n      <img src=\"https://placekitten.com/g/200/300\" />,\n      this.refs.div\n    );\n  },\n});\n\nvar container = document.getElementById('container');\nReact.render(<div><LeakyPortal key={1} /></div>, container);\nReact.render(<div><LeakyPortal key={2} /></div>, container);\nReact.render(<div><LeakyPortal key={1} /></div>, container);\n```\n\n(Works fine if you implement componentWillUnmount.)\n",
